Class CarbonUI.UIConfig.UIElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team1829.library.CarbonUI.UIConfig.UIElement
  • Enclosing class:
    CarbonUI.UIConfig

    public class CarbonUI.UIConfig.UIElement
extends java.lang.Object
    A UIElement represents a source of data from a controller. Each UIElement has a USB port which identifies which controller the control data originates from, and a controller ID which tells which specific button, thumbstick, slider, or other physical input from that controller in question.
